{
  "primitive": {
    "$description": "PointSav design system — primitive token layer. Numeric scales (10/20/.../100 for color; 1..13 for spacing; 1..6 for duration) follow the convention popularised by Carbon, Material, Polaris, Atlassian, and the broader 2020-2026 design-system field — designers arriving from any of these systems recognise the structure. Color family names, hex values, spacing values, motion curves, and type scale are PointSav-original. Semantic overrides per tenant brand live in themes/<brand>.json.",
    "$schema": "https://schemas.designtokens.org/2025-10-01/draft.json",
